Lloyd Anthonie WILLIAMS, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-6737. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 12, 2013. Case below, 520 Fed.Appx. 174 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
